The Telegraph - Calcutta : Metro

 Roadside shanties turn vice den

 Sitanshu Joardar: Why have you allowed shanties to mushroom around Yogayog Bhavan? After sunset, the area becomes a den of illicit liquor and flesh trade. There has also been an explosion in the number of streetchildren.

 This is an administrative matter and calls for police action. However, I will take it up with the civic authorities.




